e |first=A. F. |year=1945 |publisher=HMSO |location=London |edition=1st |oclc=493146758}} ** Addenda and corrigenda sheet issued, republished Roy Westlake Books with Part 3A as one volume 1989, IWM-NMP 2009.{{sfn|Wells|2011|p=68}} * {{cite book |series=History of the Great War Based on Official Documents |title=Order of Battle of Divisions: The Army Council, G.H.Q.s, Armies and Corps, 1914–1918 |volume=Part 4 |year=1945 |last=Becke |first=A. F. |publisher=HMSO |location=London |edition=1st |oclc=650201154}} ** Addenda and corrigenda sheet issued with the volume and with Military Operations: Italy. Republished Roy Westlake Books 1989, IWM-NMP 2009.{{sfn|Wells|2011|p=68}}
